新冠病毒蔓延NBA，7支球队共计14名人员确诊。
New Crown Virus Spreads NBA, 7 teams a total of 14 people diagnosed.
李晓庄。
Li Xiaozhuang.
界面新闻                      。
Interface news.
界面新闻。
Interface news.
界面新闻是中国具有影响力的原创财经新媒体，只服务于独立思考的人群。
Interface News is an original and influential new financial media in China, serving only the people who think independently.
爵士中锋戈贝尔为NBA首个新冠病毒肺炎确诊病例。
Jazz center Robert Goebbels has confirmed the NBA's first case of New Crown Virus pneumonia.
（图片来源：视觉中国）记者：李晓庄“ 截至目前，NBA共有7支球队14名人员确诊，猛龙和雷霆两支队伍宣布全队检测结果为阴性。
(Photo: Visual China) Journalist: Li Xiaozhuang "So far, 14 NBA teams have been diagnosed, the Raptors and the Thunder teams have declared the results negative.
”自爵士中锋戈贝尔确诊感染新冠病毒之后，联盟已有多支球队安排球员进行检测。
Since Sir Robert Goebbels was diagnosed with the new crown virus, the league has had several teams schedule tests.
截至北京时间3月21日，NBA共有9支球队进行了检测，其中7支队伍的14名人员确诊，猛龙和雷霆宣布全队检测结果为阴性。
As of March 21, 2008, nine NBA teams had tested positive. Fourteen of the teams were confirmed, and the Raptors and Thunder announced negative results.
万幸的是，目前所有感染病毒的球员都是轻症，或还没有表现出症状。
Luckily, all the players who have contracted the virus so far are mild or have not shown symptoms.
此外，球队在医疗资源紧缺的情况下接受检测引来了大量的批评。
In addition, the team in the face of scarce medical resources to accept the test attracted a lot of criticism.
NBA回应称，对球员群体进行全面检测，其实是保护他人健康的行为。
The NBA responded by saying that comprehensive testing of players' groups is actually protecting the health of others.
联盟不希望球员成为“超级传播者”。
The league does not want players to be "super communicators."
然而，联盟还有21支球队仍未进行检测，包括和确诊病例有过直接接触的球队，如尼克斯队、公牛队和马刺队等。
However, 21 league teams remain untested, including those that have had direct contact with confirmed cases, such as the Knicks, Bulls and Spurs.
北京时间3月18日，勇士队总经理鲍勃·迈尔斯(Bob Myers)表示，因检测试剂短缺，只有在球员出现症状后才会去做检测。
On March 18, Bob Myers, general manager of the Warriors, said a shortage of reagents meant that tests would only be done if a player developed symptoms.
感染名单如下：爵士队：北京时间3月12日，戈贝尔和米切尔相继承认自己感染新冠病毒。
The list of infections is as follows: Jazz: March 12, Beijing time, Goebbels and Mitchell admitted to contracting the new crown virus.
活塞队：北京时间3月15日，官方宣布1名球员确诊。
Piston team: Beijing time on March 15, the official announcement of a player diagnosed.
据美国媒体报道，这名球员是克里斯蒂安·伍德。
According to US media reports, the player is Christian Wood.
篮网队：北京时间3月18日，官方宣布4名球员确诊。
Basketball Team: Beijing time on March 18, the official announcement of the diagnosis of four players.
随后，杜兰特承认自己为其中一员。
Durant later admitted that he was one of them.
3月19日，篮网队官方辟谣，否认欧文、勒韦尔和丁威迪为确诊球员。
On March 19, Nets officials denied Owen, Lweir and Ding Wei as confirmed players.
掘金队：北京时间3月20日，官方宣布1位成员确诊，但未公布是否为球员。
Denver Nuggets: Beijing time on March 20, officials announced the diagnosis of a member, but did not disclose whether it is a player.
76人队：北京时间3月20日，官方宣布3名成员确诊，但未公布是否为球员。
76 team: March 20, Beijing time, the official announced the diagnosis of three members, but did not disclose whether it is a player.
湖人队：北京时间3月20日，官方宣布2名球员确诊，但没有公布具体名单。
The Lakers: Beijing time March 20, officials announced the diagnosis of two players, but did not disclose the specific list.
凯尔特人：北京时间3月20日，官方宣布1名球员确诊，斯玛特通过社交媒体承认是自己。
Celtic: Beijing time, March 20, the official announced that a player was diagnosed, Smart acknowledged through social media is himself.
